Programming Assignment 2: Subject-Specific Web Crawler

Languages/Versions Used:
	Python 2.7.11

File Structure:
	docs/: default location to store html files from crawler
	crawler.py: source code for web crawler

Dependencies:
	BeautifulSoup (HTML Parser):
	http://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/

	Install BeautifulSoup
	http://www.crummy.com/software/BeautifulSoup/bs4/doc/#installing-beautiful-soup

	Quick instructions:
		- pip install beautifulsoup4

Usage:
	python crawler.py -u URL [-q QUERY] [-docs DOCS_PATH] [-m MAX_PAGES] [-t]

	required arguments:
		-u URL           The URL from which to start the crawl

	optional arguments:
		-q QUERY         The query to find related pages
		-docs DOCS_PATH  The path where the documents are stored (default: docs)
		-m MAX_PAGES     The maximum number of pages to download (default: 50)
		-t, --trace      Include to generate a trace